plots.content: Wzruszająca historia młodego Ban Ki-moon, koreańskiego gracza, który dopiero rozpoczyna swoją przygodę ze Starcraftem 2 i postanawia dostać się do diamentu.

The story follows Eijun Sawamura, a pitcher who joins an elite school with a brilliant catcher named Kazuya Miyuki. Together with the rest of the team, they strive for Japan's storied Koushien championships through hard work and determination.

Sawamura Eijun, who is a pitcher from a country high school, gets teamed up with a catcher from a school with an elite baseball team. He decides to quit his school to attend the school that this catcher plays.
Teamed up with an elite catcher, pitcher Sawamura Eijun leaves his high school in the country to attend the catcher's high school.
